iEnigma One: Real-Life Spicy Teachers—The Great Quotations Dictionary		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iof Hangzhou No.2 High School Teachers		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iHangzhou No.2 High School has China's most distinctive high school		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iprincipal, the most unique "spicy" teachers, and the most		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iunconventional teacher selection mechanism (rumored to prefer		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
ibeautiful and handsome candidates). In its philosophy, it doesn't		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
imatter if you're a normal school graduate or your teaching skills; it		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
ionly cares about your professional level and academic background		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i(typical emphasis on substance over form). Its open culture has		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
inurtured a group of teachers whose words astonish until satisfied.		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
