ithis aerobics competition! I love watching aerobics. Those classes		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iearlier were great—showing the youth and exuberance of		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iE Zhong		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
ipeople! Some so-called elite schools only care about studying; their		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
istudents look lifeless. They can't compare to us." (Judges' table,		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
