i- "		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iE Zhong		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
istudents absolutely must not engage in romantic affairs. Group		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iinteraction only, no one-on-one interaction. Anyone caught		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
idating—caught one pair, register one pair."		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i- "Good morning students, I'm your principal Ye Cuiwei. It's drizzling		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
ioutside today, so morning exercises are canceled."		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i- "Our school has won one gold medal after another in the		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
