i		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i- "Yesterday I watched an NBA game. At the last moment, the Lakers'		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iDuncan scored—(audience roars with laughter). The principal continued,		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
isatisfied: But the Spurs' Fisher didn't give up! He hit the		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
igame-winner with 0.4 seconds left! So our students must never give up		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iin the final stretch!" (Final assembly before Gaokao)		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
