i- After starting grad school, I visited the principal. He said:		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i"Beijing Normal University is good. I'm also a master's supervisor at		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iBNU's School of Education now. Had I known, you could've applied to		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
ime!" (Hehe, glad he didn't know.) "Also, we're short on psychology		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iteachers here. When you finish your Ph.D., come try at your alma		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
imater!" (Uh... can you do fMRI experiments here?) "Why are you		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
ilaughing? Our		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iE Zhong		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
inow has all teachers holding master's degrees! I have a Ph.D.! Our		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
