iXu Chengnan		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i— Former principal, Physics Special-grade Teacher, Provincial		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iMeritorious Teacher. The opposite of his successor—diligent and		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iunassuming. Led Wu Xin'an to win Zhejiang's first International		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iOlympiad gold. Nickname: Trash-Picking Principal (for often picking up		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
itrash on campus). Classic moment: Anytime.		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i- "I refuse to believe it. Hangzhou No.2 High School insists on		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iholistic education. I'll see if our Gaokao results really suffer."		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i- "There are no bad students at HZ2, only bad teachers. Since everyone		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iadmitted was top of their school, even one falling behind is our		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
ieducational failure."		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
