i— Political Education major, then vice principal. Tall, slender, heavy		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
ismoker. Classic moment: Gesturing with five fingers spread.		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i- "In reform, we must consider the national context, even family		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
icontexts. Eh? Why are you laughing down there?"		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i- "You must use my secret weapon for essay questions: State principles		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
ifirst, then analyze; critique errors; end by stating your stance."		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
